<br>
This, of course, assuming that the percentages are updated correctly in the UI.  Assuming so, Epic Pet should have about 4500hp.  I'll re-run the same test using the other pets.  It's a lot easier knowing a fixed number (i.e. the L60 pet heal healing for 900) and determining the ratios, than it is using raw calculations that rely on an unknown variable (the pet's regen).  <br>
